'''马修·威廉姆森'''（{{lang-en|Matthew Williamson}}，{{bd|1971年|10月23日|catidx=Williamson, Matthew}}）是英国时装设计师。<ref name="guardian">{{cite web |title=Double vision |first=Hadley |last=Freeman |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/style/story/0,3605,897153,00.html |date=17 February 2003 |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |accessdate=2014-11-06 |archive-date=2003-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030618062522/http://www.guardian.co.uk/style/story/0,3605,897153,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==生平==
他于1971年10月23日出生于英格兰[[曼彻斯特|曼彻斯特]]，并在17岁前就读于[[曼彻斯特|曼彻斯特]]的[[洛雷托学院（曼彻斯特）|洛雷托学院]]。后来他搬到了伦敦并且进入了[[中央圣马丁艺术与设计学院|中央圣马丁艺术与设计学院]]，1994年从这里毕业。

==职业生涯==
他的同名时装店成立于1997年2月。同一年，威廉姆森初次进入[[伦敦时装周|伦敦时装周]]并在这里发表了“电子天使”系列。<ref name=fashionweek>{{cite web|title=Matthew Williamson|url=http://www.londonfashionweek.co.uk/designers_profile.aspx?DesignerID=213|publisher=London Fashion Week|accessdate=11 December 2012|archive-date=2014-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104063058/http://www.londonfashionweek.co.uk/designers_profile.aspx?DesignerID=213|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2002年他的作品在[[纽约时装周|纽约时装周]]展出。<ref>{{cite web|last=Alexander|first=Hilary|title=New York Fashion Week: Matthew Williamson|url=http://fashion.telegraph.co.uk/news-features/TMG3365236/New-York-Fashion-Week-Matthew-Williamson.html|publisher=Telegraph.co.uk|accessdate=11 December 2012|archive-date=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012053646/http://fashion.telegraph.co.uk/news-features/TMG3365236/New-York-Fashion-Week-Matthew-Williamson.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他位于伦敦[[五月墟市|五月墟市]]布鲁顿街28号的时装店于2004年开幕。<ref>{{cite web|last=Milligan|first=Laura|title=Today in History – April 29|url=http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/history/2009/04/donatella-versace-gave-her-verdict-on-mrs-clintons-look|publisher=Vogue|accessdate=11 December 2012|archive-date=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012062459/http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/history/2009/04/donatella-versace-gave-her-verdict-on-mrs-clintons-look|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2005年他发布了香水系列，在之后的一年他被任命担任[[艾米里欧·璞琪|艾米里欧·璞琪]]的创意总监。2007年，他的时装展被采纳进[[王子_(音樂家)|王子]]的专辑''[[地球行星(王子专辑)|地球行星]]''歌曲“切尔西·罗杰斯”的录影带中。同年，伦敦的设计博物馆为他举办了名为"马修·威廉姆森——十年时尚"的回顾展。<ref>{{cite web|title=Matthew Williamson – 10 Years in Fashion|url=http://www.easier.com/28372-matthew-williamson-10-years-in-fashion.html|publisher=Easier Lifestyle|accessdate=11 December 2012|archive-date=2014-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141106093208/http://www.easier.com/28372-matthew-williamson-10-years-in-fashion.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2008年威廉姆森被授予英国时尚大奖的"年度红毯礼服设计师"奖。<ref>{{cite web|title=Red Carpet Designer 2008|url=http://www.britishfashionawards.com/content.aspx?CategoryID=378|publisher=British Fashion Awards|accessdate=11 December 2012|archive-date=2010-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101207193524/http://www.britishfashionawards.com/content.aspx?CategoryID=378|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 在这里他也曾三次被提名为年度最佳设计师。<ref name="UTalkMarketing">{{cite web |title=Fashion designer Matthew Williamson launches e-commerce site |url=http://www.utalkmarketing.com/pages/Article.aspx?ArticleID=13996&Title=Fashion_designer_Matthew_Williamson_launches_e-commerce_site |date=18 May 2009 |work=UTalkMarketing |accessdate=2014-11-06 |archive-date=2012-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120219195614/http://www.utalkmarketing.com/pages/Article.aspx?ArticleID=13996&Title=Fashion_designer_Matthew_Williamson_launches_e-commerce_site |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2008年9月马修·威廉姆森回到伦敦全身心投入于他自己品牌的投入与扩张。他在第7季''[[天橋驕子|天橋驕子]]''中作为嘉宾客串出场。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sassybella.com/2010/01/matthew-william-to-judge-project-runway-nina-garcia-la-was-almost-impossible/ |title=Matthew Williamson to judge Project Runway; Nina Garcia "LA was almost impossible" |publisher=Sassybella.Com |date=27 January 2010 |accessdate=1 August 2012 |archive-date=2014-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140925072108/http://www.sassybella.com/2010/01/matthew-william-to-judge-project-runway-nina-garcia-la-was-almost-impossible/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>这一集在2010年1月28日播出。

2010年10月，马修·威廉姆森与MBFG签下授权协议。从此推出了新的品牌——Muse by Matthew Williamson。这个新的系列于2011年发售。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://fashionlvr.com/3482/muse-by-matthew-williamson-diffusion-line-in-the-works |title=Muse by Matthew Williamson Diffusion Line In The Works |publisher=Fashionlvr.com |date=13 October 2010 |accessdate=2014-11-06 |archive-date=2010-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101209223608/http://fashionlvr.com/3482/muse-by-matthew-williamson-diffusion-line-in-the-works |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

